n stop.</li>\r\n	<li>DMItem name: DM107 RC</li>\r\n	<li>QuadcopterItem No.: DM107</li>\r\n	<li>Frequency: 2.4GHzChannel: 4CHGyro: 6 Axis</li>\r\n	<li>Quadcopter Size: 17*14.5*6cm(folded) 28*28*6cm (unfolded)Package Size: 28.5*20*6cm</li>\r\n	<li>Quadcopter Weight: About 562g</li>\r\n	<li>Quadcopter Battery: 3.7V 900mAh (included)</li>\r\n	<li>Transmitter Battery: 2 * 1.5V AAA battery (not included)</li>\r\n	<li>Charging Time: 80-100mins</li>\r\n	<li>Flight Time: 8-10minsR/C</li>\r\n	<li>Distance: About 80 meters</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: 2MP</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '17*14.5*6cm(folded) 28*28*6cm (unfolded):6:6', 0, '2020-11-27 09:11:54'),
