(399, '112', 'TL-WR841N', NULL, 'TP Link TL-WR841N 300Mbps DSL Router - Latest Version', '2250', '2499', '2999', '131', '388', NULL, 'images/products/da97077c520ffb2849ca403da2ee40bb.jpg', '<h2>Product details of TP Link TL-WR841N 300Mbps DSL Router - Latest Version</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Brand: Tp-Link</li>\r\n	<li>Model:TL-WR841N</li>\r\n	<li>300Mbps Wifi Speed</li>\r\n	<li>Single Core CPU Processor</li>\r\n	<li>4 Fast Ethernet Port</li>\r\n	<li>2 External Antenna</li>\r\n	<li>Color: White</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><u><strong>Main Features of these Routers includes:</strong></u></p>\r\n\r\n<p>300Mbps wireless speed ideal from normal applications to HD video streaming.Two antennas greatly increase the wireless robustness and stability. 2 x 5dBi antennas greatly increase the wireless robustness and stability. N300 WiFi speed for faster downloads &amp; Internet gaming. Easy wireless security encryption at a push of WPS button. IP based bandwidth control allows administrators to determine how much bandwidth is allotted to each PC Compatible with IPv6 -the more recent Internet Protocol version. TP-LINK Tether App allows quick installation and easy management using any mobile device. Fast ethernet ports (10/100 Mbps) allow you to directly connect your wired devices. WPA/WPA2 secure your WiFi connection, Guest Network/Parent Control secure your WiFi access. TP-Link Tether app - Easily set up and manage your home network.</p>\r\n', 1, '1:6:6', 0, '2020-12-04 05:59:11'),
(400, '112', 'tp5', NULL, 'TP Link Archer C20 AC750 Wireless Dual Band Router-(Black)', '3600', '4275', '4500', '131', '388', NULL, 'images/products/e70109c1b199a10aaedaa2b127a945ea.jpg', '<h2>Product details of TP Link Archer C20 AC750 Wireless Dual Band Router-(Black)</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Wireless Type: 802.11B, 802.11G, 802.11N</li>\r\n	<li>Supports 802.11AC standard, with simultaneous 2.4GHz 300mbps and 5GHz 433mbps connections for 733mbps of total available bandwidth</li>\r\n	<li>3 external antennas provide stable Omni-directional signal and superior wireless coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless Standards: IEEE 802.11ac/n/a 5GHz, IEEE 802.11b/g/n 2.4GHz</li>\r\n	<li>Signal Rate: 5GHz: Up to 433mbps, 2.4GHz: Up to 300mbps</li>\r\n	<li>Antenna Type: 3 fixed external antennas combined with higher quality antenna technology</li>\r\n	<li>Wireless Security:64/128-bit WEP,WPA/WPA2,WPA-PSK/WPA2-PSK encryption</li>\r\n	<li>Interfaces: 4 x 10/100mbps LAN ports, 1 x 10/100mbps WAN port and 1 USB 2.0 port</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>TP-Link&rsquo;s Archer C20 comes with the next generation Wi-Fi standard &ndash; 802.11ac, backward compatible with 802.11n and 3 times faster than wireless N speeds.Archer C20 offers you the flexibility of two dedicated networks and ensures amazing wireless performance. Simple tasks such as sending e-mails or web browsing can be handled by the 2.4GHz band while bandwidth intensive tasks like online gaming or HD video streaming can be processed by the 5GHz band &ndash; all at the same time.</p>\r\n', 1, '1:6:6', 0, '2020-12-04 06:20:27'),
(401, '112', '', NULL, 'Tp-Link Archer C6 Full Gigabit Dual Band Router', '8800', '10499', '11000', '131', '388', NULL, 'images/products/9de8fb58584ab062e4662f700d729e46.jpg', '<h2>Product details of Tp-Link Archer C6 Full Gigabit Dual Band Router</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Name :Gigabit wi-fi router TP-LINK Archer C6 AC1200 MU-MIMO.</li>\r\n	<li>Brand ; Tp-link.</li>\r\n	<li>Model : Archer C6.</li>\r\n	<li>Supports 802.11ac standard</li>\r\n	<li>Simultaneous 2.4GHz 300 Mbps and 5GHz 867 Mbps connections for 1200 Mbps of total available bandwidth</li>\r\n	<li>4 external antennas and one internal antenna provide stable wireless connections and optimal coverage</li>\r\n	<li>Easy network management at your fingertips with TP-Link Tether</li>\r\n	<li>MU-MIMO achieves 2X efficiency by communicating with up to 2 devices at once</li>\r\n	<li>Supports Access Point mode to create a new Wi-Fi access point</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The Archer C6 creates a reliable and blazing-fast network powered by 802.11ac Wi-Fi technology.</li>\r\n	<li>The 2.4GHz band deliversspeeds up to 300Mbps, ready for everyday tasks like emailing and web browsing, while the 5GHz band delivers speedsup to867Mbps, ideal for HD video streaming and lag-free online gaming.</li>\r\n	<li>Wi-Fi Coverage throughout Your Home Four external antennas and one internal antenna send Wi-Fi signals to every corner of your home.</li>\r\n	<li>Stay connected and enjoy fast Wi-Fi whether you are lounging on the sofa or on the balcony.With a powerful chipset, the Archer C6 provides ideal Wi-Fi coverage.</li>\r\n	<li>The 2.4GHz band coverage is especially impressive, eliminating Wi-Fi dead-zones and beating that of other competing routers.</li>\r\n	<li>MU-MIMO lets the Archer C6 serve multiple devices at once. No more bandwidth congestion or latency. All devices get their data faster and Wi-Fi is used more efficiently!</li>\r\n	<li>With one Gigabit WAN port and four Gigabit LAN port, speeds can be up to 10&times; faster than standard Ethernet<br />\r\n	<br />\r\n	connections. Connect your favorite wired devices to the Archer C6 and get impressed!</li>\r\n	<li>The free Tether app is available for both Android and iOS devices, making it easy to set up the Archer C6 and manage your network settings.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n', 1, '1:6:6', 0, '2020-12-04 06:27:09'),
