utton and Windows Hello.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Light up your world:</strong>&nbsp;See in the dark with an optional backlit keyboard that allows you to easily type in dim-light settings, such as finding your favorite streaming content late at night in bed or traveling overnight on a plane.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Add the finishing touches</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Play with power:</strong>&nbsp;Discover seamless multitasking and stable performance on the go with the latest 11th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; processors and Intel&reg; Iris&reg; Xe graphics with up to 512GB PCIe SSDs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory matters:</strong>&nbsp;Switch back and forth between open applications easily with up to 16GB DDR4 memory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Double your display:</strong>&nbsp;Expand your view with a multifunctional USB Type-C&trade; port that supports display port, data transfer and power delivery.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart sensors:</strong>&nbsp;New adaptive thermals use advanced algorithms and accelerometers to know when your laptop is in your hands, lap or on a desk. This allows it to intelligently adapt its thermal profiles to the situation. Plus, it&rsquo;s smart enough to unleash full power when stationary on a desk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Unite your devices with Dell Mobile Connect</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Seamless PC/smartphone integration:</strong>&nbsp;Access multiple devices without dividing your attention&mdash;Dell Mobile Connect 3pairs your iOS or Android smartphone with your laptop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Limit disruptions:</strong>&nbsp;With Dell Mobile Connect, you get the option to channel notifications from phone calls, SMS, IMs and other apps right to your laptop. Keep your focus on a single screen and respond only when it&rsquo;s convenient for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Maintain your privacy:</strong>&nbsp;Your phone connects to your PC via Dell Mobile Connect&rsquo;s point-to-point, secure connection so your data is never exposed via unsecure Internet connections.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy transfer:</strong>&nbsp;Quickly move photos, videos, music and documents from PCs to Android phones, and vice-versa, without complicated cloud storage services or cumbersome cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports &amp; Slots</strong><br />\r\n1. SD Card Reader | 2. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type A | 3. Headphone/Microphone Combo | 4. Wedge-shaped lock slot | 5. Power jack | 6. HDMI 1.4b | 7. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type A | 8. USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-C&trade; (DP/Data Transfer/Power 1Delivery)</p>\r\n', 1, '14 inch:6:6', 0, '2020-12-09 12:37:21');
