(493, '118', '', NULL, 'Dell Inspiron 14 5402 i5 11th Gen | 4GB Ram | 256GB SSD | Graphics | Touch Pen', '92800', '104000', '116000', '140', '400', NULL, 'images/products/464cfad140392f16b97a8341c91776be.jpg', '<table style=\"width:268px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Display Size</td>\r\n			<td>14 inches</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Generation</td>\r\n			<td>11th</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Graphics</td>\r\n			<td>NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; MX330 2GB GDDR5</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Maximum Display Resolution</td>\r\n			<td>FHD (1920 x 1080) Anti-glare LED Backlit Non-touch Narrow Border WVA Display</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Operation System</td>\r\n			<td>Win10</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ports and connectivity</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1. MicroSD Card Reader | 2. USB 3.2 Gen 1 | 3. Headphone/Microphone Combo | 4. Power jack | 5. HDMI 1.4 | 6. USB 3.2 Gen 1 | 7. USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-C&trade; (DP/PowerDelivery)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Processor</td>\r\n			<td>Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-1135G7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Processor Speed</td>\r\n			<td>8MB Cache, up to 4.2 GHz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ram</td>\r\n			<td>4GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Series</td>\r\n			<td>Inspiron</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Storage</td>\r\n			<td>256GB SSD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Touch Screen</td>\r\n			<td>Yes</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Battery</td>\r\n			<td>&nbsp;</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Insurance</td>\r\n			<td>1 Year Insurance</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Warranty</td>\r\n			<td>1 Year Warranty</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Better battery</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Minimize the time you spend tethered to the wall and maximize your mobile lifestyle with ExpressCharge&trade;, which will recharge your battery in a flash (up to 80% in 60 minutes*).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>On in an instant:</strong>&nbsp;A built-in lid sensor allows you to open the lid and power up in a snap, no matter what power-state you are in.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Responsive by nature:</strong>&nbsp;Fast, silent and more shock resistant than hard disk drives, your Inspiron&rsquo;s PCIe NVMe solid-state drive (SSD) provides stable on-the-go performance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Watch and play all day</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Play with power:</strong>&nbsp;The latest 11th Generation Intel&reg; Core&trade; processors with Intel&reg; Iris&reg; Xegraphics (i5 and i7 only) deliver incredible responsiveness and smooth, seamless multitasking. Easily switch back and forth between open applications with up to 16GB DDR4 memory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Adaptive Thermals</strong>: New adaptive thermals use advanced algorithms and accelerometers to know when your laptop is in your hands, lap or on a desk. This allows it to intelligently adapt its thermal profiles to the situation. Plus, it&rsquo;s smart enough to unleash full power when stationary on a desk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Look good on the go.</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Comfort is key:</strong>&nbsp;A lift hinge makes for a more comfortable typing angle and improved air circulation under your device. Carry on your day in comfort, thanks to an easy-to-hold rubber hinge cap (available on Platinum Silver).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Indulge in extras:</strong>&nbsp;Sleek and clean design elements like diamond-cut edges around the touchpad and the aluminium cover and palmrest add a luxe touch. 17.9%* larger than previous generations, the touchpad provides extra room for navigation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Enjoy the view:</strong>&nbsp;See every scene in style with a beautiful FHD wide-viewing angle display encased in a narrow border. An impressive screen-to-body ratio gives you an expansive view in a sleek 35.56cm (14) body.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Customize your computer</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Show your true colors:</strong>&nbsp;Extend your own personal style to your laptop by choosing from a variety of color options. For a classic, yet contemporary, color opt for Platinum Silver. Or select Eden or Pebble for a nature-inspired and muted, yet stunning look. Plus, the angular hinge on Pebble accentuate your laptops sleek look and feel. The uniform anodized finish on the cover and hairline finish on the palmrestcome together to create a harmonious contrast and visually captivating experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optional power button and fingerprint reader:</strong>&nbsp;The newly redesigned power button is neatly incorporated into the keyboard for a sleek and streamlined look. Experience total integration with the optional fingerprint reader on the power button that allows you to log in securely with a single touch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Next-level graphics:</strong>&nbsp;Enjoy the extra power and optimal everyday performance of optional NVIDIA&reg; GeForce&reg; MX350 discrete graphics with up to 2GB GDDR5 graphics memory.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Light it up:</strong>&nbsp;Whether you&rsquo;re in bed at night watching your favorite streaming video or traveling in a dark airplane cabin, a backlit keyboard allows you to easily type in dim-light settings.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Unite your devices with Dell Mobile Connect</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Stay Focused &amp; Connected</strong><br />\r\nStay focused on tasks by interacting with your phone direct from your Dell PC&ndash; you can easily make calls, send texts, and get notifications.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Transfer Files Seamlessly</strong><br />\r\nTransfer files, photos, videos, music, and documents between your PC and phone without complicated cloud storage or cumbersome cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Mirror Device to PC</strong><br />\r\nProject your Android or iOS device screen onto your PC and interact with apps there.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Maintain your privacy</strong><br />\r\nYour phone connects to your PC via Dell Mobile Connect&rsquo;s point-to-point, secure connection so your data is never exposed via unsecure internet connections</p>\r\n', 1, '14 inch:5:6', 0, '2020-12-09 12:49:04'),
