(498, '118', '', NULL, 'Dell Inspiron 13 7306 i5 11th Gen | 8GB Ram | 512GB SSD | Touch | Win10', '135840', '152820', '169800', '140', '400', NULL, 'images/products/0d00856315587af950548aabfbb0b781.jpg', '<table style=\"width:268px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Display Size</td>\r\n			<td>13.3 inches</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Generation</td>\r\n			<td>11th</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Graphics</td>\r\n			<td>Intel&reg; Iris&reg; Xe Graphics</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Maximum Display Resolution</td>\r\n			<td>FHD (1920 x 1080) Truelife Touch Narrow Border WVA Display with Active Pen support</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Operation System</td>\r\n			<td>Wim10</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ports and connectivity</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>1. 3-in-1 MicroSD card reader | 2. 3.5mm Headphone/Microphone combination jack | 3. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A | 4. Power (4.5mm barrel) | 5. HDMI 2.0 out | 6. Thunderbolt&trade; 4 with Power Delivery &amp; DisplayPort</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Processor</td>\r\n			<td>Intel&reg; Core&trade; i5-1135G7</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Processor Speed</td>\r\n			<td>8MB Cache, up to 4.2 GHz</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Ram</td>\r\n			<td>8GB</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Battery</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<p>4-Cell Battery, 53WHr (Integrated)</p>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Storage</td>\r\n			<td>512GB SSD</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Touch Screen</td>\r\n			<td>Yes with Touch Pen</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Warranty</td>\r\n			<td>1 Year Warranty</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Insurance</td>\r\n			<td>1 Year Insurance</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n	</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Vibrant visuals:</strong>&nbsp;Take full advantage of HDR content&rsquo;s superior dynamic range with Dolby Vision&trade;, which can deliver colors never before seen on SDR PC displays. Dolby Vision&trade; content can deliver highlights that are up to 40 times brighter, and blacks that are up to 10 times darker.*</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>More screen:</strong>&nbsp;Keep your screen clear and elegant with all-around narrow borders that provide a high screen-to-body ratio. Plus, on 2-in-1s in Element Black, an optional 4K Ultra HD display provides high resolution for precise detail and images.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Back to black</strong><br />\r\nThe Element Black model of the Inspiron 13 7000 2-in-1 takes intuitive technology to a new level with these premium features:*</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Take note:</strong>&nbsp;The black model of our 2-in-1 is fully equipped with a rechargeable active pen (PN771M) that is intuitively placed inside a built-in pen garage and will charge while stored.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Designed to impress:</strong>&nbsp;Write, sketch, draw, and take notes more naturally with an updated active pen. Now with 4096 pressure sensitivity levels, tilt detection, quick-key eraser button, and Bluetooth connectivity.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Swift strokes:</strong>&nbsp;Effortlessly move the pen across the screen with the latest Microsoft Pen Protocol 2.0. It detects the slightest movements, like pen tilt, creating a more fluid experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Optimal experience: This stylus design is comfortable, expressive and functional. Its decagon profile is easy to hold and grip and won&rsquo;t roll off a desk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ready when you are</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Exceptional experience on the go:</strong>&nbsp;Intel&reg; EVO&trade; series brings the perfect combination of performance, responsiveness, battery life and stunning visuals to a new class of sleek, stylish laptops. Co-engineered with Intel to provide the ultimate experience for work or life on the go. Learn More</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Instant access:</strong>&nbsp;Staying connected with up-to-date applications has never been easier thanks to Connected Modern Standby with Voice Support. Now your device stays ready, even when asleep and allows you to call out for its voice assistant to instantly wake it up to perform a task.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ready and waiting:</strong>&nbsp;An IR camera (available on Element Black only) or easy-to-use fingerprint reader, removes the hassle of typing your password so that you can get to your desktop quickly. Plus, the lid-open sensor will turn on your laptop, even when completely off, so that you can access what you need, when you need it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ExpressCharge&trade;:</strong>&nbsp;Get your battery from 0% up to 80% in as fast as an hour* so that you&rsquo;re not tied down to an outlet while out and about.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Solid-state drive:</strong>&nbsp;The NVMe solid-state drive (SSD) means much faster system response time, quieter performance and improved shock resistance compared to conventional hard drives and is even faster than regular SATA SSDs.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Connectivity you can count on:</strong>&nbsp;With the new 802.11 AX wireless protocol, also known as WIFI 6, your Inspiron&rsquo;s WIFI transfer speeds, range and reliability works better than ever in busy coffee shops and other high-traffic areas. You&rsquo;ll also enjoy a greater range from hotspots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Beauty in the details</strong><br />\r\n<strong>Thunderbolt&trade; 4:</strong>&nbsp;A USB Type-C port supporting Thunderbolt&trade; 4 allows you to charge your laptop (Element Black only), connect to multiple devices, and enjoy data transfers of up to 40Gbps, 8 times that of a USB 3.1 Gen 1.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Smart sensors:</strong>&nbsp;New adaptive thermals use advanced algorithms and accelerometers to know when your laptop is in your hands, lap or on a desk. This allows it to intelligently adapt its thermal profiles to the situation. Plus, it&rsquo;s smart enough to unleash full power when stationary on a desk.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Advanced experience:</strong>&nbsp;Comfortable typing has arrived with an improved lift-hinge that adds a tilt to the keyboard and with better screen view&mdash;getting work done has never been more seamless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Stay secure:</strong>&nbsp;An all-new webcam privacy shutter provides security you can trust and control.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Designed to impress:</strong>&nbsp;This 2-in-1&rsquo;s striking exterior is engineered to keep you looking sleek and stylish.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>A vision in silver</strong><br />\r\nThe Platinum silver model of the Inspiron 13 7000 2-in-1 is equipped with these great features:</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Take note:</strong>&nbsp;Swift and responsive digital pen use has arrived with this 2-in-1&rsquo;s optional active pen (PN350M).* It features Microsoft Pen Protocol 1.5, which allows you to interact easily without the need to pair a pen.*</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Power button and fingerprint reader:</strong>&nbsp;The redesigned power button is neatly incorporated into the keyboard for a sleek and streamlined look. Experience total integration with the fingerprint reader on the power button that allows you to log in with a single touch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Unite your devices with Dell Mobile Connect.</strong><br />\r\nSeamless PC/smartphone integration: Access multiple devices without dividing your attention&mdash;Dell Mobile Connect pairs your iOS or Android smartphone with your laptop.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Limit disruptions:</strong>&nbsp;With Dell Mobile Connect, you can make calls, send texts, get notifications and even mirror your phone onto your PC to interact with all your favorite apps.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Maintain your privacy:</strong>&nbsp;Your phone connects to your PC via Dell Mobile Connect&rsquo;s point-to-point, secure connection so your data is never exposed via unsecured internet connections.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Easy transfer:</strong>&nbsp;Quickly move photos, videos, music and documents from PCs to phones, and vice-versa, without complicated cloud storage services or cumbersome cables.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Ports &amp; Slots</strong><br />\r\n1. 3-in-1 MicroSD card reader | 2. 3.5mm Headphone/Microphone combination jack | 3. USB 3.2 Gen 1 Type-A | 4. Power (4.5mm barrel) | 5. HDMI 2.0 out | 6. Thunderbolt&trade; 4 with Power Delivery &amp; DisplayPort</p>\r\n', 1, '13.3 inch:6:6', 0, '2020-12-09 13:23:52'),
(499, '118', '', NULL, 'Dell Inspiron 14 5490 i7 10th Gen | Graphics | Win10', '105600', '132000', '132000', '140', '400', NULL, 'images/products/243603a6144ce963ba4ac68679f7175f.jpg', '<p><strong>Fresh design</strong><br />\r\nRefined colors:&nbsp;Choose from a variety of contemporary and calming colors, like Platinum Silver and Iced Gold.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Sleek interior</strong><br />\r\nThe newly redesigned power button is neatly incorporated into the keyboard for a clean and modern look, while the optional fingerprint reader on the power button allows you to log in with one touch. The venting holes are also moved from the palmrest to the hinge for a fully streamlined design, in a laptop with a height of only 17.3mm.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Slim exterior</strong><br />\r\nAll your travel just got seamless thanks to a thin and light design. As thin as 17.3mm, your device effortlessly slips in your carry-on, backpack or bag. An aluminum top cover also gives your device a premium look and feel.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Optional backlit keyboard</strong><br />\r\nEasily type under dim light, such as when you&rsquo;re on an evening flight or need to access your device in bed, with a optional backlit keyboard.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>ExpressCharge Boost&trade;</strong><br />\r\nGo from 0% up to 35% in as little as 20 minutes* to jumpstart your laptop and not worry about hopping from power outlet to outlet. Get up to 80% charge in as fast as an hour* to be ready for your longer excursions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Wealth of features</strong><br />\r\nLatest processors: 10th Gen Intel&reg; processors deliver incredible responsiveness and smooth, seamless multitasking.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Memory and storage galore</strong><br />\r\nEasily switch back and forth between open applications with up to 8GB of memory. Store movies, photos and music with 512GB PCIe NVMe SSD storage. The PCIe NVMe SSD means much faster response time, quieter performance and improved shock resistance 