(574, '122', '', NULL, 'Realme 7i [8GB RAM // 128 GB ROM] - Capture Sharper. Play Smoother', '23995', '29990', '29990', '143', '387', NULL, 'images/products/fc49cba855f6ef8238e048caec8080ef.jpg', '<p>Product Description AI Quad Camera Enjoy capturing every moment vividly with the help of this smartphone&rsquo;s 64 MP AI quad camera. 64 MP Primary Camera The next time you are on a vacation, you can delight your loved ones to clear and vivid pictures of the picturesque surroundings, as this smartphone features a 64 MP primary camera. Super Nightscape</p>\r\n\r\n<h2>Product details of realme 7i [8GB RAM // 128 GB ROM] - Capture Sharper. Play Smoother.</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>64MP Quad AI Camera</li>\r\n	<li>90 Hz Ultra Smooth Display</li>\r\n	<li>18Watt Quick Charge</li>\r\n	<li>5000mAh Battery</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The beauty of nightlife needs to be captured in all its essence! This smartphone lets you do just that, with its Super Nightscape mode. Special Night Filters Want to give an added dose of effect to your night photos? You can utilise this phone&rsquo;s artistic night filters and show-off your gorgeous pictures to your friends. In-display Selfie This phone comes with a 16 MP in-display selfie camera. It also comes with the AI Beauty mode that lets your selfies look stunning. Oh, and the Bokeh Effect lets you, the subject, stand out against any backdrop. Ultra Smooth Display From watching your favourite videos to playing those intense games, everything will appear seamless on this smartphone&rsquo;s 90 Hz Ultra Smooth Display. With a 16.5 cm (6.5) display, you can get set for a truly immersive experience. 5000 mAh Battery You don&rsquo;t need to take a break from your entertainment just because your phone is running out of battery. This phone comes with a 5000 mAh battery. Oh, and it supports 18 W quick charging so you can have your phone back and running quickly. Super Power Saving Mode This mode allows you to use up to 6 common apps on your phone, even when the charge is below 10%. Performance Features With good power consumption control and the ability to manage heavy-duty games, this phone&#39;s Snapdragon 662 octa-core processor and 8&nbsp;GB of RAM will facilitate a great performance experience. This phone also comes with a memory capacity of 128&nbsp;GB so that you can keep all your important files without worrying about space. Gorgeous to Look At This phone&rsquo;s design has been inspired by the fusing of colours inside a watercolour pai</p>\r\n', 0, '6.5 inch:6:6', 0, '2020-12-29 20:11:15'),
