(580, '122', '', NULL, 'OPPO F17 PRO Ultra Sleek Design 6 AI Portrait Cameras 8GB RAM 128GB ROM 30W VOOC Flash Charge 4.0', '35192', '42999', '43990', '129', '387', NULL, 'images/products/234337af1bcf8d7a20fefa1c2f45d94c.jpg', '<h2>Product details of OPPO F17 PRO Ultra Sleek Design 6 AI Portrait Cameras 8GB RAM 128GB ROM 30W VOOC Flash Charge 4.0</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Ultra Sleek design</li>\r\n	<li>Ultra Thin 7.48mm</li>\r\n	<li>Weight 164g</li>\r\n	<li>Smooth Rounded Edge Screen</li>\r\n	<li>Aspect Ratio 20:9</li>\r\n	<li>High Resolution 2400x1080</li>\r\n	<li>Screen size 6.43&quot;</li>\r\n	<li>In- Display Finger Print 3.0</li>\r\n	<li>30W VOOC Flash 4.0</li>\r\n	<li>Memory 8GB RAM, 128GB ROM</li>\r\n	<li>Andriod 10</li>\r\n	<li>Color OS 7.2</li>\r\n	<li>6 Camera Phone MAIN: 48MP, 8MP, 2MP, 2MP Front: 16MP, 2MP</li>\r\n	<li>Gorila Glass 3</li>\r\n	<li>Octa core Processor</li>\r\n	<li>Mini Punch Hole Diameter 3.7mm</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/0e7c7846475041eebb68131cb4342281_17457657dcd_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Sleek and Lightweight Build</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring a thickness of 7.48 mm and a weight of 164 g, this sleek and lightweight smartphone does not feel bulky and offers a premium feel. The 220&deg; smooth rounded edges further make it a delight to hold and use this phone. It comes with a 20:9 aspect ratio, making it comfortable to use this phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/5a6e3c0a5c544e579e9d4f8c3ed8dde2_17457658e6e_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stunning Full HD+ Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone from Oppo features a 16.34-cm (6.43) Full HD+ Super AMOLED screen, with a resolution of 2400x1080 pixels, to offer a stunning, clear, and cinematic viewing experience. The mini dual punch-holes, with a diameter of 3.7 mm, help enhance the viewing area, making it a delight to watch videos and play games. Furthermore, you can quickly and securely unlock this amazing smartphone in just 0.3 seconds, thanks to the in-display fingerprint sensor 3.0.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/de7164291f8e4b53b8983b96e72031b0_1745765a0a9_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Impressive Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The striking design of this Oppo smartphone is sure to grab the attention of onlookers. This phone is fingerprint resistant, ensuring it will look stunning at all times.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/a9e0760bb1144de3965811a1dac9c097_1745765c303_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Breathtaking Photos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With this smartphone in your hand, you can click professional-quality photos and record amazing videos with ease. This phone features a total of 6 AI portrait cameras (quad-rear cameras and dual-front cameras), so you can capture breathtaking portrait pictures, anytime and anywhere.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/681f39e89ff94c6282ce0e0639bf481e_1745765d58c_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Portrait Photography Made Easy</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone comes with features, such as AI Super Night Portrait, AI Night Flare Portrait, and AI Color Portrait, which is sure to make clicking photos a whole lotta fun.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/a6bd665785be4d27be244a1f0bd4f13d_1745765e748_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture Beautiful Photos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With amazing features, such as Dual Lens Bokeh, AI Super Clear Portrait, and AI Beautification 2.0, you can click stunning pictures which are sure to leave your social media followers in awe.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d669098a12974d4cb187456ce524cee7_17457660194_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultra Clear Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can click crystal-clear pictures of a person, object, or the surroundings on this phone, thanks to the Ultra Clear mode.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d558a8ef175143d18de4635fd903f7e2_174576616ef_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Record Stunning Videos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>If you&rsquo;re a vlogger or would like to explore vlogging as a hobby, this phone will be the ideal one for you. The front and back cameras of this Oppo smartphone allow you to record smooth and steady videos, making it a delight to shoot amazing 4K videos on it, so you can showcase your passion to the world. Moreover, the Slow-Motion and Bokeh Video features help take your passion for recording videos to the next level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/5a1923db40304eaeb2cba9c4b68f8956_17457662f71_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Long-lasting Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Hosting a massive battery, this smartphone from Oppo offers a battery life of up to 10 hours. This phone&rsquo;s 30 W VOOC Flash Charge 4.0 technology lets you recharge it fully in about 53 minutes. If you&#39;re short on time, a quick 5-minute charge can offer you a talk time of up to 4 hours.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d2a73d9d6538431f8b449d341e9c1cb8_17457664373_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Night Charging</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the AI Night Charging feature, this Oppo smartphone can be charged overnight without any worries. This feature ensures that your phone is charged to 100% with battery optimizations at an AI-determined morning wake time.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/bd224007330a494ab7fda42ca3a5797d_174576659dd_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Power-saving Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even when this Oppo smartphone&rsquo;s battery is too low, you can still access up to six apps, thanks to the Super Power Saving Mode. Turn on this mode, so you can make a quick call, book a cab, or send a text to your loved one, even when the phone&#39;s battery is about 5%.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/8df32cdf24a74d418fbd2bbd3e4dca7b_17457666adb_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Powerful Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring a powerful MediaTek Helio P95 processor and 8 GB of RAM, this phone makes it easy for you to seamlessly multitask between apps, play graphics-rich games without experiencing lag, and more. The internal storage space of up to 128 GB lets you store multiple apps, photos, videos, and more. The MediaTek HyperEngine technology takes your mobile gaming experience to the next level.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d151b338d76042a98f7545810b9b69da_17457668392_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Operating System</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Enjoy a seamless and intuitive user experience as this smartphone runs on the ColorOS 7.2.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/258ebd5b57cd487ea4807c51ca60a340_17457669537_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Anti-lag Algorithm</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This algorithm helps minimize screen stuttering and freezing, making it a delight to use this phone.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/6122daf2d3ad4e3f82b8de042473ec26_1745766af0f_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Air Gestures</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can answer calls without even touching the phone or using voice commands as this Oppo smartphone can recognize air gestures from as far as 20-50 cm. All you need to do to activate this feature is by lifting your hand upwards.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>In The Box</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Handset, Headset, USB Cable (1m, White), Adapter, SIM Card Pin, Protective Case (Transparent TPU), Quick Guide, Warran