(583, '122', '', NULL, 'Oppo A52 4GB/128GB', '23995', '29990', '29990', '129', '387', NULL, 'images/products/72fb880cb003116ecc7c06573817f0eb.png', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d2f80343dac44e1fb803b9cc2f6cf839_172b79daf5e_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>FHD+ Resolution</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch videos, play games, and more by immersing yourself into this phone&rsquo;s 1080p Neo Display. With a screen-to-body ratio of 90.5% and an ultra-narrow side bezel of 1.73 mm, your visual experience is truly going to be a delight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/71c13b9eeec948f9908cae6139fb6017_172b79e3594_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Eye Care Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone can automatically adjust the screen brightness based on your habits and the ambient light around you. Oh, and with the Eye Care mode, a lot of blue light is reduced, thereby reducing the strain on your eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/8aac3c5ef8e440019d442f56fb03c5a3_172b79e9d1f_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>3D Quad Curve Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Giving it a smooth feel is this phone&rsquo;s 3D Quad Curve design featuring optimized curvature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d4802fc3b88240f481f6d2c854033ee0_172b79f044c_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Quad Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring an AI main camera with a large aperture, a 119-degree ultra-wide-angle lens, and two portrait lens, this phone&rsquo;s AI Quad Camera set-up will be an instant hit.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ae617ccd226949c38321f4bcabd24d02_172b79f87cb_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stable and Clear Videos</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Record every moment in life, in the most beautiful way possible, as this phone supports Video Anti-shake that supports clear and stable recording. What&rsquo;s more, this phone supports 4K video recording, wide-angle video, and slow-motion video function (120 fps).</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/94bfd6f7fb1b4723a419971c9b7f8a71_172b79fff55_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture Gorgeous Pictures at Night</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone, with the f/1.8 aperture lens and Night Mode 2.0, will ensure that even the photos you click during the night come out well.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/70090ae9f09a45e19597d240e662966e_172b7a09020_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Beautification</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone comes with the AI Beautification mode that matches different skin tones based on the lighting conditions and settings. It also features a more delicate skin effect and a smooth contour effect.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/37c292ba4eae41e88db75e63b546733a_172b7a0e6a8_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Memory</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone comes with the 128 GB/UFS 2.1 storage. This leads to continuous reading performance, thereby ensuring multiple apps function smoothly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/dced736f5dc04df18bf966913e1fac46_172b7a152d1_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Snapdragon and Hyper Boost</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone is equipped with the Qualcomm Snapdragon octa-core processor and OPPO&rsquo;s Hyper Boost performance that will work to increase the speed of your favourite apps for a smooth experience. It features the ColorOS 7.1 operating system.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/8b93d8ff1da443e8b93ce445822f78f3_172b7a1db02_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>5000 mAh Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>No matter how intensely you use your phone, this phone&rsquo;s 5000 mAh battery will ensure that it&rsquo;s up and running. With 18 W fast charging via the USB Type-C charging port, you can count on this phone to charge quickly.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d2a97981f62643c998c287476bc54172_172b7a232e4_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dual Stereo Speakers</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone comes with dual stereo speakers and the Dirac 2.0 sound effect which automatically identifies vides, games, and music.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/131d38fca8f048bab03fbd222f55a563_172b7a2c9e6_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Dark Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your eyes will feel comfortable while looking on the screen, thanks to the Dark mode and the Eye Care mode. These modes also aid in reducing the phone&rsquo;s overall power consumption.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/3cee740f546e4885b61b8561c89d9a37_172b7a33909_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smart Sidebar</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Quickly access everything you need with the help of the Smart Sidebar. Oh, and do you want to enter the split-screen mode? All you have to do is slide your finger, bring out the sidebar, and just drag the app that you want to use.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>In The Box</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Handset, Adapter, Headset, Micro USB Cable, Quick Guide, SIM Card Tool, Screen Protect Film, Case, Booklet with Warranty Card</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model Number</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>CPH2061</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model Name</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>A52</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Color</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Stream White</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Browse Type</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Smartphones</li>\r\n			</ul