(585, '122', '', NULL, 'Vivo Y20i (3GB RAM+ 64 GB ROM)', '16792', '20379', '20990', '144', '387', NULL, 'images/products/720fa5204f647bf5307f7c9b0ca4f3f5.jpg', '<h2>Product details of vivo Y20 (3GB RAM+ 64 GB ROM)</h2>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Display size 6.51&quot; inch HD+</li>\r\n	<li>Processor Snapdragon 460</li>\r\n	<li>Camera: Rear 13MP + 2MP + 2MP Front: 8MP HD+</li>\r\n	<li>3GB RAM/64 GB ROM</li>\r\n	<li>5000mAh Battery Micro USB Port,</li>\r\n	<li>Side Mounted Fingerprint Scanner</li>\r\n	<li>Wifi, Bluetooth , USB Type B GPS, OTG,Kids Mode ,Eye Protection Mode, Android 10</li>\r\n	<li>Funtouch 10.5</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ddcab4bcd61f43eea65de42d24b5122e_1744ecaa992_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>5000 mAh Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vivo Y20i&rsquo;s 5000 mAh super capacity battery challenges even the toughest power challenges, and it also supports OTG reverse charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/206febf71e2f44f89f0cfd8fae3e1a76_1744ecac1ff_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Side-mounted Fingerprint Scanner</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Unlocking your phone is now instantaneous and intuitive. What&rsquo;s more, the Face Wake technology now lets you unlock your phone in a split second.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/580cfd3093ef4c688a69b896811fbb78_1744ecad642_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualcomm Snapdragon Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring the Qualcomm Snapdragon processor and 64 GB of storage, the Vivo Y20i can handle large-scale games with ease. It also comes with a triple card slot and is expandable up to 256 GB.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/8a7447b77eca46a99cb3271417fef171_1744ecaea2f_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Triple Macro Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With its 13 MP triple rear camera, an f/2.2 large