(586, '122', '', NULL, 'Vivo V20 8GB Ram 128GB Rom, 64MP Back Camera, 44MP Selfie, 5000mAh Battery', '38392', '45990', '47990', '144', '387', NULL, 'images/products/312a5cbef399c726139ad33b466bbbac.png', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ed76cbd71c804d0d94e4206bfd47c701_1751b3c06e5_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>44 MP Front Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Even when you zoom to click a picture, it will come out stunning! This phone&rsquo;s Ultra HD 44 MP front camera will make sure that every selfie you click is clear and flaunt-worthy!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/92c9c52cc3254db18adb7ccfa68e392f_1751b3cacbd_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>4K Selfie Video</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 4K selfie videos, shot with this phone, will look absolutely vivid and detailed, thanks to the 4K resolution and Eye Autofocus.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ffe2fbc1852f417ba0bab721d106664d_1751b3d6a1e_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Slo-mo Selfie Video</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Switch between slow and fast motion, at 240 fps, with the help of this smartphone&rsquo;s slow-mo selfie video feature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/1656cdfbb2fb4a9493e9074efc1682cc_1751b3de528_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Steadiface Selfie Video</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Taking a video while on-the-go? This phone&rsquo;s Steadiface Selfie video will ensure that your videos come out really well with minimal blur and a steady face.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/0f006fa636494f268a1c3a4e939f6f53_1751b3e6767_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super Night Selfie 2.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vivo&rsquo;s multiple exposures and a noise-cancelling algorithm will ensure that even the selfies you click in the night turn out to be fabulous. The Aura Screen Light also paves the way for perfect colour temperature and more natural skin tones, as it will automatically adjust to the ambient light.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/0af0c7d3f04344c39f83c6527df376e9_1751b3f2e99_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>64 MP Main Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Vibrant details, even after zooming-in! That&rsquo;s how this phone&rsquo;s 64 MP main rear camera will click your images! The supporting rear cameras will ensure that you get to shoot with a wider perspective, take better close-up shots, and even make use of bokeh and black and white effects to give your pictures a dash of personalisation.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/cc2b0b1af6564fb58456e07d6edc1b7f_1751b3fa3c0_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super Night Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone&rsquo;s Super Night Mode will give your night pictures the vibrance they need by adding untapped perspectives and specialised filters.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/59dacc960f42415dba05f4ebe321c815_1751b4012cd_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Motion Autofocus</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Wondering how you can keep the focus on a running object? All you have to do is double-tap on the moving object and the Motion Autofocus will track it so that it remains sharp throughout the video!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/7f24695801c34111b826ede4e8826d4d_1751b40e129_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Matte Glass Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Slim and light! This phone&rsquo;s design will leave its spectators pleasantly surprised with its gorgeous design.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/e3f482d7f9a34c42bcbf7550a0095605_1751b4143f6_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AMOLED FHD+ Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Watch everything with vibrant details on this smartphone, thanks to its AMOLED FHD+ display.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ac54902cee4442c489e196b6d7ab9669_1751b41cf14_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Qualcomm Snapdragon 720G</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With 8 GB of RAM and the Snapdragon 720G mobile platform, this smartphone has everything in place for a seamless performance. It comes with an internal memory capacity of 128 GB so you can have all your files and documents stored in your phone itself.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/a28aca2fb1614e67b8d33880a06c514f_1751b42e970_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>FlashCharge</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone supports 33 W FlashCharge so you can have your device juiced-up quickly. Oh, and the 4000 mAh battery will ensure that your phone is up and running whenever you need it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/fa702e24cf5f49f083ea4d3e05d82168_1751b435591_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Android 11</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone&rsquo;s Funtouch OS 11 (based on Android 11) has a simple aesthetic that will facilitate an effortless user experience.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>\r\n\r\n<table>\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>In The Box</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Handset, Earphones, Type C to USB Cable, USB Power Adaptor, SIM Ejector, Protective Case, Protective Film (Applied), Documentation</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model Number</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>V2025</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Model Name</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>V20</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Color</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Midnight Jazz</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>Browse Type</td>\r\n			<td>\r\n			<ul>\r\n				<li>Smartphones</li>\r\n			</ul>\r\n			</td>\r\n		</tr>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<td>SIM Type</td>\r\n			<td