(587, '122', '', NULL, 'Vivo V20 SE(8GB RAM/128GB ROM)', '30400', '36892', '37999', '144', '387', NULL, 'images/products/c8e5ea66c1cf2b745f7adb57bdd53be3.jpg', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/7065d03555b94d5fa8cf5855136d1d4c_17587a2cad0_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>3D Slim Body</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a thickness of 7.83 mm and a weight of 171 g, this phone is a slim and light one to carry around. You can even hold it comfortably in your hand.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d77a8d9bd51a49e0bc7c51b7dc194401_17587a3478a_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>32 MP Front Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Incredible details are what will make your precious moments being captured look perfect! This phone&rsquo;s 32 MP front camera is equipped to do just that - make your memories look great!</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/2bc11eebe62e4e15bc5accc2e4d97695_17587a3e3d3_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super Night Selfie</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This phone&rsquo;s HDR+ Morpho algorithm brightens dark spots and will reduce overexposure in highlights so that your night-time pictures come out really well with the right amount of balance, clarity and brightness.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/082d1687534f4c4cbb835fc0f9d41572_17587a455bb_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Triple Rear Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The 48 MP main rear camera, the 8 MP wide-angle camera, and the 2 MP bokeh camera will make your pictures of almost everything around you look spectacular.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/086d842878ac4a3f83896e831d943939_17587a6bd86_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super Night Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The large f/1.8 aperture of the main rear camera, assisted by HDR+ Morpho algorithm, will ensure that the stunning night