(591, '122', '', NULL, 'Vivo Y30 (4GB RAM // 64GB ROM)', '20000', '22499', '24999', '144', '387', NULL, 'images/products/20892514734fb2fdde002b6d0301e19a.png', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/038d004fae2d4f43b440151f3cd31932_17301077e24_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>iView Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Featuring a 16.44 cm (6.47) display, with a minimal-sized front camera, this phone from vivo makes it a delight to view photos, browse the Web, and watch videos. Moreover, its 90.7% screen-to-body ratio, with an aspect ratio of 19.5:9, makes this phone a visual delight.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/e93edff1de6f4c8f9e5d60e372472cf9_1730107d354_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Large Storage</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the 64&nbsp;GB internal storage, this phone lets you install multiple apps and also lets you store your favorite memories in the form of photos and videos. The large storage capacity of this smartphone ensures that you won&rsquo;t have to delete files or your favorite gaming apps to make space for new data.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/43d4826a373747bc855c8436bd65efc2_1730107c18d_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Long-lasting Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stay entertained for long hours while you&rsquo;re traveling or waiting at the airport as you can easily play games for about 9 hours or listen to your favorite albums for about 137.09 hours on a single charge, thanks to this smartphone&#39;s large battery capacity of 5000 mAh.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/cb98b4e5951945a08d3d9c9e5063f522_17301085650_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>AI Quad Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone from vivo comes with a quad-rear camera setup, featuring a 13 MP main camera, an 8 MP super-wide-angle camera, a 2 MP super-macro camera, and a 2 MP bokeh camera, so you can capture and record high-quality photos and videos like a pro.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/77aa0268125642ae830d73d461c9b611_1730108404a_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super-wide-angle Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With a 120&deg; horizontal view, the 8 MP super-wide-angle camera helps you capture more in one click. You can easily take photos of larger groups of people, wider landscapes, and larger cityscapes with this smartphone&rsquo;s super-wide-angle camera.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/f7baf87bb960471ea514d0c6d5475d5b_173010885a7_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Super-macro Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture the minute details of an object clearly on this smartphone, thanks to the super-macro camera. The 4-cm focus lets you capture sharp and close-up images of objects, like a butterfly&rsquo;s wing, dewdrops on a leaf, and much more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d1d4623d19fc4d70b1098c1ffdf04dff_17301086abb_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Multi-Turbo 3.0</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This vivo smartphone boasts the Multi-Turbo 3.0 feature that has been updated with the industry&#39;s first VPG (vivo Process Guardian) technology and uses Centre Turbo to deliver enhanced speeds by scheduling the core system&#39;s resources. Also, AI Turbo helps in making intelligent judgments.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/51e715f1c32640399179dde7bddfc864_1730108adf4_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ultra Game Mode</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With Competition Mode, this smartphone from vivo ensures that gaming-enthusiasts can experience a seamless and immersive gaming experience. Moreover, you can record winning moments or other important moments during a game, thanks to this smartphone&rsquo;s Screen Recording feature.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Specifications</p>\r\n\r\n<p>General</p>