(593, '122', '', NULL, 'POCO X3 (6 GB RAM/ 128 GB ROM) 6.67&quot; FHD+ Display phone with Snapdragon 732 G Processor', '25600', '31999', '31999', '145', '387', NULL, 'images/products/b7c074ade7270cd325fae08c20fa6e87.png', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ad2c6c27591646698c54cd5afbeb1b44_174de730081_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>As Powerful As It Gets</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone packs a Qualcomm Snapdragon 732G processor and an Adreno 618 GPU that make just about everything you do on this phone seamless.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/98a6ca2b00b541ecb68acd63359a6951_174de7340f0_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Smooth Visuals</p>\r\n\r\n<p>While its 120-Hz refresh rate makes the visuals a treat to watch, its display&rsquo;s 240-Hz touch sampling rate offers responsiveness that can take your gaming as well as overall smartphone experience up a notch.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/e0420d683a0e47d3b32fa4671d134728_174de582c82_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Massive Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its 16.94-centimetre (6.67) FHD+ Display, 2400x1080 resolution, 20:9 aspect ratio, 91.25% screen-to-body ratio, and its HDR10 feature work in harmony to make your favourite video content all the more enjoyable. In addition, its TUV Rheinland Low Blue Light Certification ensures that the content you&rsquo;re watching is flicker-free and doesn&rsquo;t strain your eyes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/c5182c046f504bddb49714684dc94c64_174de738b9c_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Battery That Lasts</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Your gaming and entertainment needs are well taken care of as this phone boasts a 6000-mAh battery. On a single charge, you can enjoy up to 14 hours of gaming, 31 hours of videos, and 45 hours of VoLTE calling. And, if when you exhaust its battery, you can charge it back in a jiffy as it supports 33 W Fast Charging and features the MMT Technology, which makes for up to 26% faster charging.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/1aef60ed9f3644beb81cf1bd9922fd25_174de773781_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>For the Photographer in You</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its connected quad-camera set-up includes a 13-megapixel ultra-wide-angle camera, 2-megapixel macro camera, 2-megapixel depth camera, and finally a 64-megapixel front camera to help you capture all kinds of pictures, ranging from landscapes to close-ups. Also, its 119&ordm; field of view and amazing AI Filters help you get those wide shots and add some uniqueness to your photos. On top of that, you can even enjoy taking selfies with its 20-megapixel AI Selfie Camera when you&rsquo;re in the mood for it.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/1900e4117d8545818bc687350c9a78ea_174de76a690_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Incredible Heat Dissipation</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone features LiquidCool Technology Plus, along with Multi-layer Graphite and LiquidCool Heat Pipe, to facilitate 3D heat dissipation, so you don&rsquo;t have to stop gaming due to overheating-related woes.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/618cba2ef4714a3fa361d072f3054857_174de744c0f_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Punchy Sound</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Its Hi-Res Audio certified Dual Stereo Speakers deliver crisp yet powerful sound from both ends to make your aural experience more immersive.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/2456b1a0b90d4a3fafbbac99f0ced580_174de5268ee_image.png?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Innovative Design</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This POCO handset&rsquo;s ergonomy and metallic lustre help you use it comfortably while getting some heads to turn. It&rsquo;s Side-mounted Fingerprint Sensor and Power Button, al