(596, '122', '', NULL, 'Samsung S20 FE 6.5&quot; Full HD+ AMOLED Display 8 GB RAM/ 256 GB', '63635', '79540', '79540', '118', '387', NULL, 'images/products/ae91a2a9f0fb8594e00bb62a3a71c1fb.jpg', '<p>Product Description</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/721233996fcf46ceba3557dd8589513a_1757504796d_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>A Smartphone You Will Love</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Be it for gaming, clicking photos, recording videos, or checking your social media feeds, the Samsung Galaxy S20 FE smartphone helps you do all these and more. Stylish and elegant, this smartphone from Samsung is sure to be every gadget freak&rsquo;s must-have device.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/40c4c2370349439083f5724b8f3c707d_1757865154f_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Stunning Colors</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The Samsung Galaxy S20 FE comes in a myriad of stunning colors and finishes, so you can flaunt this stunning device wherever you go. From classic and subtle hues to bold and eye-catchy colors, you can buy this smartphone in the color of your choice.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/cdc0263ea7694d8abd74e39ecf929c02_1757504b56f_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Infinity-O Display</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Get ready to enjoy an immersive and cinematic viewing experience as this smartphone comes with a 16.40 cm (6.5) Full HD+ Infinity-O display. Moreover, its narrow bezels, flat edges, and a small punch hole for the camera offer you a larger viewing area, making it a delight to binge-watch TV shows, capture images, play games, and more.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/3e3dcc7369c043618bbabd6d204a1b9e_175786656b2_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Triple Rear Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The rear camera setup of this smartphone comprises three cameras (12 MP + 12 MP + 8 MP) so that you can capture stunning and professional-like photos of landscapes, food, and people with ease. The 12 MP Ultra Wide Camera and the 12 MP Wide-angle Camera let you capture a larger view of landscapes and cityscapes. The 8 MP Telephoto Camera offers up to 3x Optical Zoom capabilities for close-up shots.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/9431ca2d41a740fa97f0c513ab53d046_17575054d6b_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>30x Space Zoom Feature</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Thanks to the combination of up to 3x Optical Zoom and up to 30x Super Resolution Zoom, you can easily capture close-up images of a subject/object even when you&rsquo;re at a distance.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/e1db655024a744099914bdf2d2279773_1757505689b_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Capture Images Even in the Dark</p>\r\n\r\n<p>You can capture stunning pictures even in dimly lit environments (Night Mode turned on), thanks to the dual-pixel sensor and enhanced camera AI of the rear camera setup. The dual-pixel sensor helps add more light to the images, so your shots are clear and vivid. It also simultaneously captures multiple frames, thereby processing the images into a single clear night-time photo.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/f0c4ca00a6bd49e6ae72810e36b61c28_17575058462_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Single Take Feature</p>\r\n\r\n<p>With the Single Take feature, this smartphone offers you multiple photo and video options, helping you create stunning content for your social media accounts. All you have to do is, shoot a particular scene for about 15 seconds, and let the smartphone convert them into videos, photos, and more. You can find them in the smartphone&rsquo;s Gallery app.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/7ebdcc462b4a4198b052242897084bb7_17575059a9d_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>32 MP Front Camera</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Step up your selfie and vlog game as this smartphone comes with a 32 MP front camera. Every image that you capture and every video that you record using the front camera will be clear and vivid.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/74a752d0f7284971b81e22ed4ac80313_1757505b066_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Easy Connectivity</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone supports LTE networks, with speeds of up to 1.6 Gbps, so you can enjoy a seamless browsing and streaming experience. Moreover, thanks to Wi-Fi 6 connectivity, you can achieve fast data speeds, with low latency, even if you&rsquo;re in a crowded area. So, irrespective of whether you&rsquo;re connected via the mobile network or Wi-Fi, you can play online games or stream videos from the Web while experiencing minimal lag.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/11a90de32dff405a9fc0648f7b944c13_1757505c3c5_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Fast Refresh Rates</p>\r\n\r\n<p>This smartphone from Samsung features a Super AMOLED display that has a refresh rate of up to 120 Hz, so you can enjoy a fast and smooth scrolling experience. So, whether you&rsquo;re browsing through the day&rsquo;s tweets on Twitter or scrolling through Instagram feeds, you can smoothly scroll through them without experiencing screen stuttering.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/d908258fe2ec4e178532d5a36a709f06_1757505de0c_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Long-lasting Battery</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Equipped with a massive 4500 mAh battery, this Samsung smartphone lets you chat with your friends, play games, listen to music, watch videos, and do more in a day before it has to be charged again.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><img src=\"https://rukminim1.flixcart.com/image/200/200/cms-rpd-images/ad5da45198dc4db0a070c4d2cbf77e82_1757505efc3_image.jpeg?q=90\" /></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Powerful Processor</p>\r\n\r\n<p>From switching between ap